  "definitions": {
    "e-label": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "CONCLUSIONS",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug",
      "marginBottom": "0.5rem"
    },
    "e-now": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### What Designers Can Do Now\n\nEnvironmental impact in design is not a future concern — it is a present-tense professional practice. Most of the interventions that reduce footprint also improve performance: smaller assets, less JavaScript, lighter animations, better caching.\n\nThe profession does not lack tools. It lacks a shared norm that treats environmental cost as a design constraint alongside performance, accessibility, and maintainability.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.45,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "e-checklist": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Project Checklist\n\n**Assets** — All images compressed and served as WebP/AVIF. Video lazy-loaded with appropriate posterframes.\n\n**Fonts** — Variable fonts preferred. Subsetting applied. Max 2 typefaces per project.\n\n**Animation** — Motion justified by UX function. No looping animation on idle screens.\n\n**Hosting** — Green hosting provider confirmed. CDN edge caching in use.\n\n**Measurement** — Page weight budgets set at project start. Website Carbon Calculator run before launch.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.45,
            "delay": 0.08
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "e-reading": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Further Reading\n\nLevin, T. — *Sustainable Web Design* (A Book Apart, 2021)\n\nWebsite Carbon Calculator — websitecarbon.com\n\nSustainable Web Manifesto — sustainablewebmanifesto.com\n\nGreen Web Foundation — thegreenwebfoundation.org\n\nONS — *UK Digital Carbon Footprint Report* (2023)\n\nW3C — *Sustainability Guidelines* (Draft, 2023)",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.16
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
